onsidered when methotrexate is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/35962/', '', 'Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, More', 'Tinidazole, Furazolidone, Quinacrine, Secnidazole, Artesunate, Mefloquine, Lumefantrine, Artemether, Tafenoquine, Halofantrine, Quinine, More', 1767369485);
