s of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/36028/', '', 'Tropicamide, Ephedrine, Ketorolac, Phenylephrine', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Trimethobenzamide, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 1767369485);
